latestIgtvVideos.title: SPF reapplication hack ☀️
latestIgtvVideos.caption:
Reapplying SPF on top of my makeup using the @beekman1802 Milk Primer! I saw this hack and had to try it out. Sometimes the spf powders can be too drying for my skin so this was a great reapplication hack!
